The Last Light Survival Guide — Licensing
==========================================

This project is dual-licensed to separate the *software* from the *content*:

1. CODE  — the HTML/CSS/JavaScript, build scripts, and infrastructure templates
   are licensed under the **MIT License**. See the `LICENSE-CODE` file.

2. CONTENT — the written survival/reference material, text, and diagrams authored
   for this project are licensed under the **Creative Commons
   Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License (CC BY-SA 4.0)**.

3. BUNDLED WORKS — the bundled reference books and data retain their own original
   licenses (public domain or their respective CC licenses). The Hesperian Health
   Guides are CC BY-SA non-commercial — keep them free. See the README for the
   list of incorporated sources.


